    "Name": "Unexpected Transmission",
    "Details": "<color=#BFBFBF>Darius’s voice cuts through the intercom, urgent and strained.</color>\n\n“Commander, get to the conference room. You’ve got a call coming in—and trust me, this one’s unexpected.”\n\n<color=#BFBFBF>He’s already waiting when you arrive, arms crossed, tension clear on his face.</color>\n\n“It’s about those mechs. The ones from the convoy op. Someone claims they’ve got information.”\n\n<color=#BFBFBF>The comm panel blinks, waiting to be answered. Whoever’s on the line might be the first real lead you’ve had since this whole mess began.</color>",
